Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.15,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,You’re really yearning all the time, aren’t you, Lain?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.73,0:00:04.86,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.40,0:00:07.60,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I’m envious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.60,0:00:10.77,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Human perception is a wild thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.77,0:00:14.35,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,If you start feeling something, you start believing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.35,0:00:18.40,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I don't know how to explain to anyone that I am really me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.04,0:00:25.20,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,But being able to question that sense of self is a special talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.73,0:00:28.22,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,I don’t want a talent like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.22,0:00:29.17,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.17,0:00:32.28,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I’m sure you feel really strongly that way right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.06,0:00:37.71,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,But I feel that it can be a good thing for you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.71,0:00:47.22,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I don't understand it well right now, but I think that if you can include and accept that as part of yourself, it would help you in the long run.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.22,0:00:49.31,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,I won’t change?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.31,0:00:50.95,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.95,0:00:56.64,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,You might change naturally and stop having nightmares.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.64,0:01:00.13,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,If that happens, you’d be like most other kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.13,0:01:06.22,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,But I won’t know if I’ve gotten better. I might have nightmares again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.22,0:01:10.48,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Yeah. But things will change from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.48,0:01:12.28,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.28,0:01:18.84,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I mean that you’re not alone. I’m here and you can talk to me about things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:21.73,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,That’s true, Touko-san.
